\b
\q1 Reintaim yu olataim sandim rein,
\q1 La kolweja na yu sandim det dyu.
\q1 Yubin meigim det san la skai.
\q1 Yubin meigim olting ebriweya.
\b
\q2 Yu haibala, Dedi God. Yubin sandim yu ron san.
\q2 Na gibit yu Spirit la melabat,
\q2 Bla mela wokabat gudbalawei
\b
\q1 Brom oldentaim yubin bos la wi,
\q1 Bat basdam wi nobin sabi yu neim.
\q1 Tidei na mela sabi gudnyus:
\q1 God im dedi bla melabat.
\b
\q2 Yu haibala, Dedi God. Yubin sandim yu ron san.
\q2 Na gibit yu Spirit la melabat,
\q2 Bla mela wokabat gudbalawei
\b
\qr Words by Margaret Sharpe. Tune: Gurludu (Peaceful Dove), @ Margaret Sharpe 1985. 
